data.description: Here's your chance! Location, location - charming 3 bedroom bungalow within walking distance of Clifton Heights Park. Large & inviting covered front porch with extra wide steps has welcoming curb appeal! This great home features 3 bedrooms, a nice size kitchen with a separate dining room for entertaining AND main floor laundry! Third bedroom currently functions as an office/laundry space (washer and dryer are in the over-sized closet). LARGE level, fenced-in backyard is the perfect hangout spot for BBQs, pets, gardening+++ Full basement with walk-out waiting for your finishes! This home has it all, situated in a popular STL neighborhood, w/ easy access to local parks, shops, restaurants, highways & entertainment options! Would also make an awesome rental property opportunity $$$, priced to sell! CALL NOW for more information.
